table in\nexoplanetary atmospheres, have low false positive potential, and would provide\nstrong evidence for life in conjunction with other well established\nbiosignature candidates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2022 18:22:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 17:37:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-17"}
