 consensus ranked our TopoCP method as the best\nsegmentation in 100\\% of the cases with a high inter-expert agreement. Overall,\nboth quantitative and qualitative results, on a wide range of gestational ages\nand number of cases, support the generalizability and added value of our\ntopology-guided framework for fetal CP segmentation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2022 07:14:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-17"}
